{"title":"Bronquiolitis obliterante","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neumología/Bronquiolitis obliterante-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Bronquiolitis obliterante","guid":"CW6dxHNRydNohi22Ms7AFA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Perlas","guid":"ckqwjhWYoBs6975LW0uH5g","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"¿Qué es la bronquiolitis\\Nobliterante?","guid":"IKbs42SePfYKTeOOU4or_Q","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"BO es una enfermedad de las vías aéreas pequeñas caracterizada por inflamación y\\Nfibrosis que llevan al estrechamiento y obliteración de los bronquiolos.","guid":"aTemMlGQAuli6CK_KK4UiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"¿Cuáles son los\\Nsíntomas principales?","guid":"","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Disnea progresiva y\\Ntos no productiva.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"fXylDQTPWbo7BBexCxBgjQ","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Reseña histórica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"El término 'bronquiolitis obliterans' fue usado por patólogos\\Npara describir dos patrones distintos de enfermedad de vías\\Naéreas pequeñas. Hoy, se reconoce como bronquiolitis\\Nobliterante o bronquiolitis constrictiva.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"Concepto actual","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Proceso inflamatorio crónico que afecta los\\Nbronquiolos, resultando en su obliteración.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"GcApPyqVJiFuISTAPf2bRg","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Fisiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Los bronquiolos permiten el paso\\Nde aire hacia los alveolos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Lesión e inflamación del epitelio\\Nbronquiolar → ↑ Fibroproliferación →\\NEstrechamiento/Obliteración.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"11","text":"Objetivos terapéuticos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Reducción de la inflamación y\\Nprevención de la fibrosis.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"11","text":"Investigación futura","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Identificación de nuevos biomarcadores y\\Nterapias inmunomoduladoras.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"T7UJ6BcwlkElRfn-VA317Q","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Internacional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Incidencia aumenta en pacientes post\\Ntrasplante pulmonar y HSCT.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"Chile","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Datos limitados, pero se observa en\\Ncontextos de exposición ocupacional y\\Npost infecciones respiratorias.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"Morbimortalidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Alta morbilidad; mortalidad asociada a\\Ninsuficiencia respiratoria.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"20","text":"DALYs","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"No hay datos específicos.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo","guid":"REDap3XATYRfdEeaHDK4mA","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Trasplante pulmonar/HSCT","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Edad avanzada, incompatibilidad\\NHLA, reflujo gastroesofágico.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"Exposición a tóxicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Fuegos industriales, productos\\Nquímicos (ej. diacetilo).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"Causas","guid":"UEIUZ2opgOlkr-KLOXm6mQ","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text"